title: Provisions) Order 2021 (S.I. No. 334 of 2021) is amended by the substitution of
heading: 2. The Data Sharing and Governance Act 2019 (Commencement of Certain
text_raw:
2. The Data Sharing and Governance Act 2019 (Commencement of Certain 
Provisions) Order 2021 (S.I. No. 334 of 2021) is amended by the substitution of 
the following for Article 3: 

“3. The 16th day of December 2022 is appointed as the day on which 
subsections (2) and (3) of section 6 of the Data Sharing and Governance 
Act 2019 come into operation.”. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

23 March, 2022. 

MICHAEL MCGRATH, 

Minister for Public Expenditure and Reform. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 25th March, 2022.
